# Declarative state-directory management for CoordiNode.
# Processed by systemd-tmpfiles on boot and on package install/upgrade.
# Reference: tmpfiles.d(5).
#
# Type Path                       Mode UID         GID         Age Argument
# Top-level state dir; the data/ subdirectory is created lazily by systemd
# (StateDirectory= in coordinode.service) so it stays out of the package
# file list and tracks the unit's lifecycle on uninstall.
d     /var/lib/coordinode         0750 coordinode  coordinode  -   -
